sta, quinoa, nuts.<\/li><li><strong>B12<\/strong> &#x2013; Solved by eating eggs, cottage cheese, soy substitutes, oats. <\/li><li><strong>Omega 3 <\/strong>&#x2013; Solved by eating walnuts, flaxseed oil, rapeseed oil, chia seeds.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.mayoclinic.org\/healthy-lifestyle\/nutrition-and-healthy-eating\/in-depth\/vegetarian-diet\/art-20046446\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Make sure you&#x2019;re getting the right nutrients<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103735\/how-to-become-vegetarian-restaurants.jpg\" alt=\"how to become vegetarian restaurants\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"how to become vegetarian restaurants\" class=\"wp-image-51374 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103735\/how-to-become-vegetarian-restaurants.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103735\/how-to-become-vegetarian-restaurants-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103735\/how-to-become-vegetarian-restaurants-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103735\/how-to-become-vegetarian-restaurants-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/s