l veggie cookbooks. You&#x2019;ll be surprised at how inventive, tasty, and colorful vegetarian food can be!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Some great Cookbooks &amp; Instagram accounts are:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/global-vegan-ellie-bullen\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">The Global Vegan<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/alexafuelednaturally\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Alexa Fuelled Naturally<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/deliciouslyella\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Deliciously Ella<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103759\/becoming-vegetarian-breakfast-1080x746.jpg\" alt=\"becoming vegetarian breakfast\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"311\" alt=\"becoming vegetarian breakfast\" class=\"wp-image-51366 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103759\/becoming-vegetarian-breakfast-1080x746.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103759\/becoming-vegetarian-breakfast-300x207.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103759\/becoming-vegetarian-breakfast-600x414.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103759\/becoming-vegetarian-breakfast-800x553.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103759\/becoming-vegetarian-breakfast-450x311.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103759\/becoming-vegetarian-breakfast-1536x1061.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103759\/becoming-vegetaria