r noopener\">The Game Changers<\/a> (totally inspiring!)<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.netflix.com\/title\/80216393\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">David Attenborough: A life on our planet<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.netflix.com\/title\/80033772\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Cowspiracy<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Did you know?<\/strong>&#xA0;By following a vegetarian diet for one year you can<a href=\"https:\/\/dealsonhealth.net\/vegetarian-statistics\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> reduce your carbon footprint in the same way<\/a> as if you didn&#x2019;t drive your car for a whole 6 months!<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104523\/travel-from-home-tips-netflix-1080x718.jpg\" alt=\"travel from home tips netflix\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"299\" alt=\"travel from home tips netflix\" class=\"wp-image-49758 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104523\/travel-from-home-tips-netflix-1080x718.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104523\/travel-from-home-tips-netflix-300x199.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104523\/travel-from-hom