lock-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-7-find-restaurants\">7. Find Restaurants<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>You might even be surprised at the number of vegetarian options on the menu of your favorite restaurant. No doubt, being vegetarian has become easier than ever, with creative restaurants popping up in cities all over the world. This means that wherever you are, you should be able to find a delicious meat-free dining alternative!&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Replacements:&#xA0;<\/strong>If the restaurants don&#x2019;t offer any vegetarian options, ask if it&#x2019;s possible to switch out meat for another product.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113902\/bar-botanique-best-cafe-amsterdam-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"bar botanique best cafe amsterdam\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"bar botanique best cafe amsterdam\" data-id=\"34966\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113902\/bar-botanique-best-cafe-amsterdam.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/travel-blog\/amsterdam\/attachment\/bar-botanique-best-cafe-amsterdam\/\" class=\"wp-image-34966 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/2