, a huge amount of grain and water is required to produce meat. In fact, 1600(!) liters of water are used to make <a href=\"https:\/\/www.mondaycampaigns.org\/meatless-monday\/benefits\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">one quarter-pound beef burger<\/a> compared to only 148 liters for a pound of vegetables!&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel-1080x719.jpg\" alt=\"sustainable travel\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"sustainable travel\" class=\"wp-image-21453 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel-1080x719.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel-800x533.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel-1536x1023.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel-1440x959.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel.jpg 1920w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel-1080x719.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-other-benefits\">Other Benefits:<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Better health:<\/strong> Go vegetarian, lower your blood pressure, reduce the risk of diabetes and heart disease, and boost your mood!<\/li><li><strong>It&#x2019;s cheaper:<\/strong> Buying meat can be expensive. Moving to a plant-based diet is a lot cheaper, especially if you buy your veggies from a local greengrocer.<\/li><li><strong>It&#x2019;s easier for traveling: <\/strong>When you&#x2019;re traveling, it can be hard to know the source of your meat, and it can be a strain on your travel budget. Fruits and veggies also have a longer shelf-life, which is great if you&#x2019;re camping or on a road trip.<\/li><li><strong>Creativity in the kitchen:<\/strong> Moving away from meat can encourage you to develop your recipes and skills when cooking.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"