th. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103719\/vegetarian-food-delicious-1048x810.jpg\" alt=\"vegetarian food delicious\"><\/noscript><img width=\"437\" height=\"338\" alt=\"vegetarian food delicious\" class=\"wp-image-51378 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1048px) 100vw, 1048px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103719\/vegetarian-food-delicious-1048x810.jpg 1048w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103719\/vegetarian-food-delicious-300x232.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103719\/vegetarian-food-delicious-600x464.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103719\/vegetarian-food-delicious-776x600.jpg 776w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103719\/vegetarian-food-delicious-437x338.jpg 437w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103719\/vegetarian-food-delicious-1536x1187.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103719\/vegetarian-food-delicious-30x23.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103719\/vegetarian-food-delicious-163x126.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103719\/vegetarian-food-delicious-233x180.jpg 233w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103719\/vegetarian-food-delicious-768x594.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103719\/vegetarian-food-delicious-1024x791.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103719\/vegetarian-food-delicious-1397x1080.jpg 1397w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103719\/vegetarian-food-delicious-1863x1440.jpg 1863w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103719\/vegetarian-food-delicious.jpg 1920w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103719\/vegetarian-food-delicious-30x23.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103719\/vegetarian-food-delicious-1048x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-vegan\">Vegan<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Following a vegan diet is slightly more challenging than vegetarianism. Same as being vegetarian, you don&#x2019;t eat meat, poultry, or fish. On top of that, you also avoid dairy products, eggs, or other animal products, shampoo, honey, toothpaste. (Don&#x2019;t worry, you have great substitutes!)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-partial-vegetarian\">Partial vegetarian<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A partial vegetarian doesn&#x2019;t eat meat but does eat some animal foods. For example, <strong>Pescatarians<\/strong> eat fish but avoid all other meat. Or <strong>Pollo-vegetarians<\/strong> eat poultry but avoid other meat and fish.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-pescatariansim\"><strong>Pescatariansim<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>We personally found that pescatarian suited us best while traveling to get all of our nutrients. Eating fish does provide some excellent nutrients, such as Omega 3 and Vitamin B12. We eat fish once every two weeks.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Note:<\/strong> Check the origin of your fish. Overfishing is a problem, so because of that do your best to find a good sustainable\/freshly caught fish.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-flexitarian\">Flexitarian<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>And finally, Flexitarian, where you follow a plant-based diet but occasionally include small amounts of meat, dairy, eggs, poultry, or fish.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103748\/best-food-canggu-bali-secret-spot-524x810.jpg\" alt=\"best vegetarian food\"><\/noscript><img width=\"219\" height=\"338\" alt=\"best vegetarian food\" data-id=\"51371\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103748\/best-food-canggu-bali-secret-spot.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=51371\" class=\"wp-image-51371 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 524px) 100vw, 524px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103748\/best-food-canggu-bali-secret-spot-524x810.jpg 524w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103748\/best-food-canggu-bali-secret-spot-300x464.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103748\/best-food-canggu-bali-secret-spot-600x928.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103748\/best-food-canggu-bali-secret-spot-388x600.jpg 388w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103748\/best-food-canggu-bali-secret-spot-219x338.jpg 219w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103748\/best-food-canggu-bali-secret-spot-994x1536.jpg 994w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103748\/best-food-canggu-bali-secret-spot-19x30.jpg 19w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103748\/best-food-canggu-bali-secret-spot-105x163.jpg 105w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103748\/best-food-canggu-bali-secret-spot-116x180.jpg 116w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103748\/best-food-canggu-bali-secret-spot-497x768.jpg 497w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103748\/best-food-canggu-bali-secret-spot-662x1024.jpg 662w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103748\/best-food-canggu-bali-secret-spot-699x1080.jpg 699w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103748\/best-food-canggu-bali-secret-spot-932x1440.jpg 932w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103748\/best-food-canggu-bali-secret-spot.jpg 1242w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103748\/best-food-canggu-bali-secret-spot-19x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23103748\/best-food-canggu-bali-secret-spot-524x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure><\/li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133625\/things-to-do-cusco-food-1-626x810.jpg\" alt=\"cusco peru best restaurants\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"cusco peru best restaurants\" data-id=\"15543\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/stat